item.description:
The new Global Phone Numbers Catalog API lets you search for available numbers to purchase and to manage active numbers.
LIST List all active phone numbers. Optionally filter by PhoneNumber, Geography, and Type (e.g. local, mobile, tollfree, shortcode.)
